The paper focuses on compressed data structures for efficiently storing and querying large string dictionaries, which is a topic related to data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of these data structures in web mining and RDF datasets, which are areas related to computational complexity (cs.CR) and computational geometry (cs.CC).
